  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HUM aid Afghanistan 2017</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Pr&#xED;spevok pre Afganistan 2017</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;V s&#xFA;vislosti s konferenciou o pomoci Afganistanu v Bruseli v okt&#xF3;bri 2016, minister ZVaEZ SRodovzdal certifik&#xE1;t deklaruj&#xFA;ci poskytnutie finan&#x10D;n&#xE9;ho pr&#xED;spevku v sume 50 tis&#xED;c Eur.Prv&#xE1; &#x10D;as&#x165; pr&#xED;spevku v hodnote 25 000 Eur sa poskytne na dostavbu &#x161;kolsk&#xE9;ho are&#xE1;lu ne&#x10F;aleko mesta Mazar-e-Sharif. Afganistan je krajina s najni&#x17E;&#x161;ou &#xFA;rov&#x148;ou vzdelania a preto je najm&#xE4; z&#xE1;kladn&#xE9; vzdel&#xE1;vanie prioritou afgansk&#xE9;ho ministerstva &#x161;kolstva.O&#x10D;ak&#xE1;van&#xFD;m v&#xFD;stupom finan&#x10D;nej pomoci je otvorenie/vyu&#x17E;&#xED;vanie &#x161;kolsk&#xE9;ho are&#xE1;lu od nasleduj&#xFA;ceho &#x161;kolsk&#xE9;ho roku (marec 2018). Z&#xE1;kladn&#xFA; &#x161;kolu by malo nav&#x161;tevova&#x165; cca 300 det&#xED;, ktor&#xE9; doposia&#x13E; nemali mo&#x17E;nos&#x165; form&#xE1;lneho vzdel&#xE1;vania. Bolo dohodnut&#xE9;, &#x17E;e zvy&#x161;n&#xE1; &#x10D;as&#x165; finan&#x10D;n&#xFD;ch prostriedkov (25 000 Eur) bude poskytnut&#xE1; a&#x17E; na z&#xE1;klade monitorovacej misie z&#xE1;stupcov Ekumenickej slu&#x17E;by Ozbrojen&#xFD;ch s&#xED;l SR.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;With regard to the conference held in october 2016 in Brussels, Minister of the Foreign and European Affairs of the Slovak Republic promised a financial contribution to Afghanistan in a total amount of 50 000 Eur. The first part of the package in a total amount of 25 000 Eur covers a new primary school, which should be open in march 2018. Around 300 children should attend the school.&#xA0;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
